		    <td colspan="3" width="100%" align="center">
		    <font face="verdana" size="2">One of the pleasures of traveling upon the open sea and visiting the tropics is the excitement at seeing one of these.  The thrill of running for your life with no where to actually run TO is exhilarating, as well as hearing the screams of your fellow adventurers as the madman picks them off one by one.  Don't attempt to solo these under level 15, and make sure you have a group of at least 3 level 11's.  The loot list above is only semi-comprehensive.</font></td>
